ccre.cluck

Interface CluckChannelListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    CluckEncoder.AvailableListener, CluckNetworkedClient

    public interface CluckChannelListener
    A listener for data sent over a Cluck channel. Can be registered with a specific channel name or with all channels.
    See Also:
    CluckNode

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void receive(java.lang.String channel, byte[] data)
      Called when data has been received on a specific channel.

    • Method Detail

      • receive

        void receive(java.lang.String channel,
           byte[] data)
        Called when data has been received on a specific channel. Should not modify data because it is the same array sent to all instances of this function.
        Parameters:
        channel - The channel that the data was received on.
        data - The data that was received.
